  "texts": [
    "Gene mutations can cause a variety of diseases, and circRNAs regulate gene expression by competitively binding to miRNAs.",
    "Therefore, circRNAs that interact with disease-causing genes may also be associated with target diseases.",
    "Based on this, a heterogeneous circRNA-gene-disease network can be used to measure circRNA-disease associations.",
    "We downloaded circRNA-gene associations and disease-gene associations from http:// cssb2. biolo gy.",
    "edu/ knowg ene/ search. html."
  ],
